# AI Gateway - Professional Design System

## CRITICAL DESIGN RULES

### ❌ NEVER USE:
- Tailwind default gradient colors (from-blue-500 to-blue-600)
- Rainbow colored cards or components
- Multiple bright colors in one view
- Hardcoded hex values
- Inline styles
- More than 2-3 colors per component

### ✅ ALWAYS USE:
- Monochromatic design with subtle accents
- Design tokens from tailwind.config.ts
- Professional color palette (bg, text, border classes)
- Consistent spacing and typography
- Subtle animations and transitions
- Glass effects sparingly

## COLOR SYSTEM

```css
/* Primary Palette */
primary: '#3b82f6' - Main brand color
primary-hover: '#2563eb' - Hover state only
primary-foreground: '#ffffff' - Text on primary

/* Neutral System */
bg: '#fafafa' - Main background
bg-secondary: '#f5f5f5' - Section backgrounds  
bg-muted: '#f0f0f0' - Hover states
bg-card: '#ffffff' - Card backgrounds

text: '#1f2937' - Primary text
text-secondary: '#374151' - Secondary text
text-muted: '#6b7280' - Muted text

border: '#e5e7eb' - Default borders
border-hover: '#d1d5db' - Hover borders

/* Semantic (Use Sparingly) */
success: '#10b981' - Success states only
warning: '#f59e0b' - Warning states only
error: '#ef4444' - Error states only
accent: '#8b5cf6' - Secondary accent
```

## COMPONENT PATTERNS

### Cards
```tsx
// ✅ CORRECT
<div className="bg-card rounded-xl border border-border p-6 
                hover:shadow-lg hover:border-primary/20 
                transition-all duration-normal">
```

### Buttons
```tsx
// Primary
className="px-4 py-2 bg-primary text-white rounded-lg 
          hover:bg-primary-hover active:scale-[0.98] 
          transition-all duration-fast"

// Secondary  
className="px-4 py-2 bg-bg-secondary text-text rounded-lg
          border border-border hover:bg-bg-muted
          transition-all duration-fast"

// Ghost
className="px-4 py-2 text-text-secondary hover:text-text
          hover:bg-bg-secondary rounded-lg
          transition-all duration-fast"
```

### Status Indicators
```tsx
// Use subtle backgrounds with colored text/icons
<div className="bg-success/10 text-success">
<div className="bg-warning/10 text-warning">
<div className="bg-error/10 text-error">

// NOT bright colored backgrounds
```

### Animations
```tsx
// Transitions
transition-all duration-fast    // 150ms
transition-all duration-normal  // 200ms
transition-all duration-slow    // 300ms

// Hover scales
hover:scale-[1.02]  // Cards
hover:scale-[1.05]  // Small elements
active:scale-[0.98] // Buttons

// Shadows
shadow-sm hover:shadow-md
shadow-md hover:shadow-lg
```

## TYPOGRAPHY

```css
Font: Inter (system fallback)
Sizes: text-xs, text-sm, text-base, text-lg, text-xl, text-2xl, text-3xl
Weights: font-normal, font-medium, font-semibold, font-bold
Colors: text-text, text-text-secondary, text-text-muted
```

## SPACING

Use consistent spacing scale:
- p-2 (8px), p-3 (12px), p-4 (16px), p-6 (24px), p-8 (32px)
- gap-2, gap-3, gap-4, gap-6
- space-y-2, space-y-4, space-y-6

## LAYOUT PRINCIPLES

1. **Visual Hierarchy**: Clear distinction between primary, secondary, tertiary
2. **White Space**: Generous padding and margins
3. **Alignment**: Consistent grid and flexbox patterns
4. **Responsive**: Mobile-first, works on all screens
5. **Accessibility**: Proper contrast, focus states, ARIA labels

## FILE STRUCTURE

```
/app
  /dashboard - Dashboard pages
  /admin - Admin pages
  /(auth) - Auth pages
  layout.tsx - Root layout
  page.tsx - Home page

/components
  /ui - Reusable UI components
  /features - Feature-specific components
  sidebar-navigation.tsx
  providers.tsx

/lib
  /hooks - Custom React hooks
  /utils - Utility functions
  /api - API client functions
```

## CODE STYLE

- TypeScript with strict mode
- Functional components with hooks
- Named exports for components
- Proper error boundaries
- Loading and error states
- Optimistic updates where appropriate

## PERFORMANCE

- Lazy load heavy components
- Use Next.js Image for images
- Implement proper code splitting
- Minimize bundle size
- Cache API responses appropriately

## EXAMPLES OF GOOD PATTERNS

### Professional Stats Card
```tsx
<div className="group bg-card rounded-xl border border-border p-6
                hover:shadow-lg hover:border-primary/20 
                transition-all duration-normal">
  <div className="flex items-start justify-between">
    <div>
      <p className="text-text-muted text-sm">Label</p>
      <p className="text-2xl font-bold text-text mt-1">Value</p>
      <p className="text-sm text-text-secondary mt-2">
        <span className="text-success">↑ 12%</span> vs last period
      </p>
    </div>
    <div className="p-3 bg-bg-secondary rounded-lg 
                    group-hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
      <Icon className="h-5 w-5 text-text-secondary 
                       group-hover:text-primary" />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
```

### Clean Table Row
```tsx
<tr className="border-b border-border hover:bg-bg-secondary/50 
               transition-colors">
